The All New 2025 Mercedes Benz Electric G-Wagon is very much still a G-Wagon...This vehicle has a lot of modern upgrades. Thanks to Mercedes-Benz for sending over this G580 with EQ Technology.

Check out the Segway Max G3 Here - https://store.segway.com/ninebot-kickscooter-max-g3?utm_source=unbox_therapy&utm_medium=youtube also available at Amazon and Best Buy.
